transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Hello. Haan.
Customer: Sir, Shivam baat kar raha hu IndiaMART se. Kaise hain sir?
Executive: Kahan se?
Customer: IndiaMART head office se account manager aapka sir.
Executive: Haan bolo.
Customer: Sir, aapki taraf se video meet ka request aaya tha Saturday ko. Aapne interest bhi diya channel panel pe registration option try kiya tha video meet ka.
Executive: Us din office close tha so aaj humne Monday ko aaye the humne subah bhi call karne ki koshish ki aap. To koi query thi sir aapko?
Customer: Nahi nahi usko cancel kar do koi baat nahi.
Executive: Koi dikkat nahi hai hum ticket close kar sakte hain?
Customer: Haan?
Executive: Hum complaint code close kar sakte hain aapko koi issue nahi hai main keh raha tha.
Customer: Haan please.
Executive: Achcha sir, ke alawa services ko aap hi dekh rahe ho ya koi aur dekh raha hai?
Customer: Main hi dekh raha hu.
Executive: To call vagaira jo aa rahi hai wo sari perfect aa rahi hai client ki?
Customer: Haan aa rahi hai.
Executive: Achcha achcha achcha. Aapke sath koi video meet karna cha rahe the kafi din se nahi hua tha to discuss kar sakte the koi kabhi aapke team mein koi banda hoga jisse hum contact kar sakte hain baat kar sakte hain?
Customer: Kis bare mein?
Executive: Regarding your services kyunki aap naye hai do mahine se hamari dobara kyunki ek bar aapki welcome call hui thi uske bare mein aur cheeze kya implement karni kya services mein improvement lana hai. D rank hai ek do pade hue hain jisme jis category ko aap aapke product list mein add nahi hai fir bhi wo aapke nahi nahi theek hai.
Executive: Thoda sa hame cheezon ko samajhne ke liye agar aap time aapki team se koi de sake to it will be help. Haan main baad mein aapko baat karunga koi.
Customer: Theek hai theek hai theek hai aapki complaint main close kar de raha hu aapki koi abhi query nahi hai na?
Executive: Okay. Theek theek.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer requested to cancel the video meet request.



Resolution:

- Executive agreed to close the video meet request.

- Executive inquired about the services and call quality.



Next Steps: 

- None



Alert (If Any):

None

- Neutral -> Neutral



@@@Key Topics:
